Brooklyn Ave., north from and including Herkimer, to and including Fulton Streets. The view shows The Fulton Street Brooklyn Manhattan Transit Elevated Lines. In the background, is seen the Tompkins Ave., Congregational Church.

June 2, 1929.

P. L. Sperr.
